{"tid":1949260,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(行動)打擊藍店嘅機會嚟喇- 投訴藍店違反<<預防及控制疾病條例>>新規例","createTime":"2020-03-29T13:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T06:24:26.000Z","uid":353200,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ce1bbf81650e90353bb5a4adb93a127556a326","tid":1949260,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"參考文章<br />\n主旨:xxxx餐館違反《預防及控制疾病條例》規例<br />\n(上款)電子報案中心/食物環境衞生署<br />\n<br />\n2020年3月27日起行政長官林鄭月娥為防武漢肺炎疫情進一步擴散， 於當日在《預防及控制疾病條例》下新增兩條規例-「禁止多於4人在公眾地方的群組聚集」及「管制餐飲業務及若干處所的營運」. 本人於今天外出時， 發現XXXX(涉事餐館名稱)餐館並未遵守條例， 希望貴執法部門能協助跟進有關事件.<br />\n<br />\n就附件可見, 該店舖並未有遵守新條例「管制餐飲業務及若干處所的營運」-內枱與枱之間有1.5米距離，或要有其他分隔安排之規定. 除此之外， 我們亦可以留意到， 該店舖未有安排人手於店外守候， 為進入店舖的人量度體溫， 違反了「管制餐飲業務及若干處所的營運」-進入食肆時要量體溫之規定.<br />\n<br />\n本人要求貴執法部門履行責任， 前往涉事店鋪進行檢測， 並且於2020年4月 3日前進行處理及答覆(要求投訴部門在某日子前處理給答覆)。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">香港市民 謹覆</div><br />\n<br />\n2020年3月29日(寫信日期)<br />\n(證據)附件:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbzZKaP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbzZKaP.jpg&h=9d3b0fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟中文攞2， 寫得唔好請隨意更正。<br />\n以下ig同樣有文章可供分享<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B-Uay7Lg-8z/?igshid=lugv59bi5jk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-Uay7Lg-8z%2F%3Figshid%3Dlugv59bi5jk&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=63f77f82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-Uay7Lg-8z%2F%3Figshid%3Dlugv59bi5jk&h=400ceeaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B-Uay7Lg-8z/?igshid=lugv59bi5jk</a>"},{"pid":"00fa551301bf1afdec4fb0b685036ebbe96a2a83","tid":1949260,"uid":353200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:48:19.000Z","msg":"只要各位發現藍店有以下違規情況:<br />\n食肆座位不超過正常提供座位一半<br />\n枱與枱之間有1.5米距離，或要有其他分隔安排<br />\n每枱不可多於4人<br />\n食肆內人士須戴口罩，進食期間除外<br />\n進入食肆時要量體溫<br />\n食肆要提供消毒潔手液<br />\n<br />\n就可以寫信去電子報案中心， 食物環境衛生署去進行投訴店舖違反規<br />\n<br />\n各位投訴時謹記寫清楚邊間店舖違反規， 寫清楚日期地址， 同影低證據作為附件送上， 同埋要要求投訴部門喺某日子前回覆<br />\n<br />\n屋宇署 (舉報建築條例/樓宇安全衛生/ 投訴服務或政策)如果發現藍店違反建築條可以喺屋宇署投訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/bd0001/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feform.one.gov.hk%2Fform%2Fbd0001%2Ftc%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=3fe2fd76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/bd0001/tc/</a><br />\n<br />\n電子報案中心<a href=\"https://www.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/CCC/PolicePublicPage?language=ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FCCC%2FPolicePublicPage%3Flanguage%3Dch&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=a61ddc15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/CCC/PolicePublicPage?language=ch</a><br />\n<br />\n食物環境衞生署 (暫時由1823代替)<br />\nenquiries@fehd.gov.hk"},{"pid":"f85a15355b0b7e91b14e9b0569258b985cef01f2","tid":1949260,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"1823<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f0322dcca1af4dcfbffd6651f56ccb1c9c5edb80","tid":1949260,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"29408f6f81ae9bdc87a8ddf9136f2540ce7d6e84","tid":1949260,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7782c85fbbf9ac6851975c57afba4742210e6026","tid":1949260,"uid":326123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"一定選擇性執法, 剩係攪D黃店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe2222324e1c3cf38f2f87c